47:04.321 --> 47:05.155
Remember?

47:07.574 --> 47:10.369
Okay. Um... So love and dating?

47:11.453 --> 47:14.498
I love to read about it,

47:14.581 --> 47:17.626
and it's fun to write about

47:17.709 --> 47:20.003
and to think about in my head, but...

47:22.047 --> 47:23.215
when it's real...

47:25.884 --> 47:27.261
What, it's scary?

47:29.137 --> 47:30.138
Yeah.

47:31.682 --> 47:33.976
