that you let into your life,

47:39.982 --> 47:42.442
the more that can just walk right out.

47:46.655 --> 47:48.824
Just like... Like your mom, right?

47:55.330 --> 47:57.207
Uh, did you know that...

47:58.917 --> 48:00.419
my dad left us?

48:00.502 --> 48:02.671
Yeah. That was a while ago, right?

48:04.715 --> 48:05.799
Two summers ago.

48:07.134 --> 48:10.512
He's got a new wife and kid now.

48:11.638 --> 48:12.681
