I don't usually talk about it.

48:16.018 --> 48:19.771
I just felt like maybe you'd understand
'cause of your mom.

48:19.855 --> 48:22.524
Not that
it is anywhere near the same thing.

48:22.608 --> 48:25.819
No, it's totally fine.
I completely understand.

48:27.946 --> 48:30.324
Yeah, it's... It's hard, huh?

48:32.242 --> 48:33.243
It's whatever.

48:34.328 --> 48:37.748
We don't have to talk about it,
but it's not whatever.

48:40.417 --> 48:45.047
I think it's funny,
you say you're scared of commitment

48:45.130 --> 48:46.465
and relationships,

48:47.382 --> 48:50.886
but you don't seem to be afraid
to be with me.

48:52.512 --> 48:55.265
