49:03.982 --> 49:07.319
Right, of course, Lara Jean Covey,

49:07.402 --> 49:11.531
ladies and gentlemen, you can count on her
to be honest, always.

49:12.532 --> 49:13.533
Wait, Peter?

49:13.825 --> 49:16.286
-Are we cool?
-Yeah, we're fine, Covey.

49:16.745 --> 49:19.665
