50:10.382 --> 50:11.550
[phone beeps]

50:19.516 --> 50:22.436
Fake dating Peter was getting easier
and easier.

50:22.519 --> 50:24.855
I always ate with him in the cafeteria

50:24.938 --> 50:27.691
and was even becoming friends
with some of his friends.

50:28.900 --> 50:30.152
Don't touch my fries.

50:30.235 --> 50:33.363
