51:11.026 --> 51:15.363
you're like the sweet, innocent girl,
and he's a complete dick.

51:15.614 --> 51:16.615
I don't get it.

51:16.698 --> 51:21.328
You know you make me sound really boring,
right, Josh? I'm not that innocent.

51:22.287 --> 51:23.288
Okay.

51:24.539 --> 51:25.540
Okay!

51:26.541 --> 51:30.462
Well, great. If that was the reason
you came over to talk to me...

51:30.545 --> 51:32.422
No, it's... I... Wait.

51:33.757 --> 51:34.633
Look...

51:38.512 --> 51:40.889
Did you mean what you wrote in the letter?

51:42.641 --> 51:45.811
I don't know. Okay?
It was a long time ago.

51:45.894 --> 51:47.646
Well, not for me, alright?

51:47.729 --> 51:52.109
This is all new, so like, I'm...
I'm trying to understand here.

51:52.192 --> 51:55.862
