54:19.005 --> 54:19.839
Okay.

54:19.923 --> 54:22.217
I think they would be good friends.

54:22.968 --> 54:24.928
Probably. Yeah.

54:27.514 --> 54:30.934
Hey, I'm really sorry
about what my mom said to you.

54:31.643 --> 54:32.894
No, it's okay.

54:33.728 --> 54:38.149
