and I get so mad I'm glad he's gone.

55:17.272 --> 55:18.565
You don't mean that.

55:20.442 --> 55:23.028
You can be mad at someone
and still miss them.

55:28.033 --> 55:30.243
I bet you really miss your mom, huh?

55:32.829 --> 55:33.830
Yeah.

55:34.247 --> 55:35.248
Every day.

55:37.334 --> 55:38.585
But you know, it's...

55:39.919 --> 55:42.255
